    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play up to wave 20 of the first game mode!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 of 49 Turrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 of 96 Perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fewer mods &amp; mutations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All 70 weapons!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/8d06092514e656792f4a1bec542c5b99.avif?t=1728580140\" width=616 height=77 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/9f419f0c6693fe0dac25029dac53d354.poster.avif?t=1728580140\" width=616 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/9f419f0c6693fe0dac25029dac53d354.webm?t=1728580140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/9f419f0c6693fe0dac25029dac53d354.mp4?t=1728580140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Dive into a microscopic alien world, radiating with bioluminescent life and unspeakable horrors.</strong> The free demo will give you a taste of what's in store in the full game - try out all 70 of the base game's weapons, get to grips with the weapon-combining mechanics, and research permanent upgrades  <strong>(you'll keep your progress &amp; unlocks in the full game!)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/b50bbe372a8ce75948764dd17ee65091.avif?t=1728580140\" width=616 height=77 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/cd7c0ff7e21832f4ae0e72a33f691439.poster.avif?t=1728580140\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/cd7c0ff7e21832f4ae0e72a33f691439.webm?t=1728580140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/cd7c0ff7e21832f4ae0e72a33f691439.mp4?t=1728580140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Pair DNA nucleotides Adenine (rapidfire), Cytosine (precision), Guanine (spread), Thymine (explosive) to discover wild hybrid bioweapons!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bomb + Shotgun</strong> combines explosives with spread to create <strong>Blast Shotgun!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bomb + Bomb</strong> doubles down on explosive power to make <strong>Bazooka!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blast Shotgun + Shotgun</strong> forms the all-powerful <strong>Flak Cannon!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn more about each weapon and microbe from the in-game database containing all your discoveries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/a2553e6b8cf1533a705ed3ef663622d1.avif?t=1728580140\" width=616 height=77 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/d237fb3da359521062407403fd284eb3.poster.avif?t=1728580140\" width=616 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/d237fb3da359521062407403fd284eb3.webm?t=1728580140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/d237fb3da359521062407403fd284eb3.mp4?t=1728580140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mutations</strong> alter the challenges you face each run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All 75 Bassy Electronic Tunes</strong> from the Full Game  adapt to the current mood &amp; intensity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessibility Options</strong> for colourblindness and motion sickness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cloud Save</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plays great on Steam Deck!!!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/8e9ae984353d531b612e90e3853f7805.avif?t=1728580140\" width=616 height=77 /></span></p>",
